#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_composite_array.py:87
msgid ""
"``vtkCompositeArray`` stores multiple sub-arrays and presents them as a "
"single virtual array using O(log n) binary search for element access. This "
"Python mixin adds numpy integration: arithmetic, reductions, indexing, and "
"``to_numpy()`` — delegating to per-sub-array operations to minimize "
"materialization."
msgstr ""

